WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
This is Match Pulse Rooms: a second screen that helps football fans feel the match and understand why.

00:08.000 --> 00:19.000
Live-score apps tell you what happened. Betting apps show a price. Match Pulse turns scores, events, and market movement into one transparent momentum story.

00:19.000 --> 00:34.000
The Pulse is not a win probability or betting tip. Territory, threat, market shift, and recent events each show their contribution, so fans can challenge the signal.

00:34.000 --> 00:46.000
The interactive replay makes the product judgeable at any time. Score, Pulse, Tension, chart, and room narrative move together.

00:46.000 --> 00:59.000
Fans make a free full-time call with no wallet, stake, token, or prize. Crowd-versus-market makes disagreement part of the experience.

00:59.000 --> 01:09.000
Every swing connects to a timeline moment. The same engine can power publisher embeds, club communities, stadium screens, and creator rooms.

01:09.000 --> 01:24.000
For live data, the server adds protected TxLINE credentials, fetches scores and odds, and returns a narrow room model. Credentials and raw feeds never reach the browser.

01:24.000 --> 01:30.000
No wagering. Just a better way to read the game together.
